---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@components/Container.astro";
---

<Layout title="About" description="About Gift Mphuthi">
  <Container>
    <div class="space-y-10">
      <section class="animate space-y-4">
        <h1 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">About</h1>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-black/80 dark:text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            I'm an AI-focused backend engineer building production-grade multi-agent systems, RAG pipelines, and LLM-powered workflows at enterprise scale.
          </p>
          <p>
            My path into tech was WeThinkCode_ straight out of high school. Since then I've worked on production systems where AI isn't a demo. It connects to business workflows, respects auth boundaries, handles failure, and is observable enough for teams to trust it.
          </p>
          <p>
            I'm drawn to the parts of AI engineering where things usually break: tool routing, retrieval quality, context management, evaluation, fallbacks, and the handoff between model decisions and backend systems. Prototypes are easy. I build for production.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="animate space-y-4">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Current</h2>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-black/80 dark:text-white/80">
          <p>Currently at MTN building production AI systems across multiple operating companies.</p>
          <p><strong>Stack:</strong> TypeScript/NestJS, Python, PostgreSQL, Redis, Docker, Azure/AWS, OpenAI &amp; Anthropic APIs, MCP, OpenTelemetry, Datadog</p>
          <p><strong>Based in:</strong> Johannesburg, South Africa</p>
          <p><strong>Open to:</strong> Full-time backend/AI engineering roles (remote or Johannesburg).</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
